      <title>美国3月份职位空缺跌至三年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-job-openings-fall-three-year-low-march-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[3月份美国职位空缺降至三年来的最低点，而辞职人数也有所下降，劳动力市场状况缓和的迹象随着时间的推移可能有助于美联储对抗通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-job-openings-fall-three-year-low-march-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 14:22:59 GMT</pubDate>
