      <title>美国4月制造业衰退；支付的价格接近两年高位</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-manufacturing-sector-regresses-april-prices-paid-near-two-year-high-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国制造业在上个月短暂扩张后，由于订单下降，4 月份出现收缩，而工厂投入品支付的价格指标则接近两年高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-manufacturing-sector-regresses-april-prices-paid-near-two-year-high-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 14:02:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
