      <title>飞机租赁商 DAE 今年将接收一半承诺的波音飞机</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/aircraft-lessor-dae-set-receive-half-promised-boeing-planes-this-year-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飞机租赁公司迪拜航空企业 (DAE) 资本的首席执行官周三表示，该公司今年从波音公司收到的飞机数量可能仅为波音公司最初承诺交付数量的一半左右。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/aircraft-lessor-dae-set-receive-half-promised-boeing-planes-this-year-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 13:46:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果报价被拒绝，空客准备关闭A220工人</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/airbus-ready-lock-out-a220-workers-if-offer-rejected-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社看到的消息人士和调解人的建议，如果周三最新的合同报价被拒绝，空客准备将其加拿大 A220 工人拒之门外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/airbus-ready-lock-out-a220-workers-if-offer-rejected-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
