      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-private-payrolls-beat-expectations-april-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国4月份私人就业人数增幅超过预期，表明劳动力市场在第二季度初保持了增长势头。]]></description>
